# QC shim: an ontology that imports base + transform + the legislative-horizon T-Box.
# Merged with the demo A-Box + reasoned via ROBOT/ELK (offline, through import-catalog.xml).
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
<https://w3id.org/rockworx/horizon-qc/full> a owl:Ontology ;
    owl:imports <https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq>,
        <https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/transform>,
        <https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq/horizon> .
